### 📦 2. Production Release Logs (`RELEASES.md` or GitHub Tags)

Use these compilation notes to document your recent version changes for deployment tracking:

```markdown
# Production Deployment Release Log Matrix

## [v2.0.0] — Modern Reset & Engine Stabilization
### 🪐 Final Optimization Layer Deployment — 2026-05-30

### ⚡ Added & Optimized
- **Client-Side Denormalized Join Injection Engine**: Overhauled `js/upload.js` and `js/wall.js` to write account parameters directly to the post object. This eliminates cascading background network lookups, solving feed freeze frames and lag completely.
- **Persistent Credential Locks**: Added explicit `browserLocalPersistence` authorization pipelines, keeping profile contexts securely stored across browser tab terminations.
- **Parallel Swaps Tracking Systems**: Configured `Promise.all()` batch execution channels within `js/swaps.js` to update incoming, outgoing, and mutual connection fields simultaneously.

### 🎨 Design & Structural Layout Adjustments
- **Minimalist Logo-Only Header Sidebar**: Removed all text titles from side and top bars, setting the layout to focus purely on the clean square graphic asset (`logo.png`).
- **Centered Timeline Post Hierarchy**: Reset the layout to a classic social media structure. Images render cleanly at a 1:1 aspect ratio right on top, while avatar indicators and metadata flow nicely beneath the content block.
- **Decoupled Settings Panel Matrix**: Moved theme toggles, session logout actions, and database record cleanup utilities to a separate `settings.html` page to prevent layout congestion.
- **GPU Layer Layering**: Added hardware rendering metrics (`will-change: transform`) to layout containers to keep browser execution frames hovering at a smooth 60fps.

---

## [v1.1.0] — Multi-Column Prototypes & Core Testing
### 🧪 Experimental Structural Refactoring Phase — 2026-04-15

